12-06-2012 (release 0.6) ------------------------------------------------------

- YUV file filter recognizes not only ".yuv" but also ".y4m" as valid YUV
  videostream extensions.
- Support for YUV 4:2:0 and YUV 4:4:4 formats added to original YUV 4:2:2
  format support.

28-06-2007 (release 0.5) ------------------------------------------------------

- Full source code documentation (Javadoc format).

06-06-2007 (release 0.4) ------------------------------------------------------

- NullPointerException due to incomplete configuration fixed
- NullPointerException due to incomplete random option configuration setup
  fixed
